verses.text: Oh clap \w your|strong="H1121"\w* hands, all you nations. Shout \w to|strong="H1121"\w* God \w with|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H1121"\w* voice \w of|strong="H1121"\w* triumph!

\w For|strong="H3605"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* Most High \w is|strong="H3605"\w* awesome. \w He|strong="H3605"\w* \w is|strong="H3605"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* great King \w over|strong="H3605"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* earth.
\w He|strong="H3588"\w* subdues nations \w under|strong="H5921"\w* \w us|strong="H5921"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* peoples \w under|strong="H5921"\w* \w our|strong="H3068"\w* feet.

\w He|strong="H7272"\w* chooses \w our|strong="H5971"\w* inheritance \w for|strong="H8478"\w* \w us|strong="H3816"\w*, \w the|strong="H8478"\w* glory \w of|strong="H5971"\w* Jacob \w whom|strong="H5971"\w* \w he|strong="H7272"\w* loved. \qs Selah.\qs*

God \w has|strong="H5159"\w* gone up \w with|strong="H5159"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* shout, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w with|strong="H5159"\w* \w the|strong="H3290"\w* sound \w of|strong="H1347"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* trumpet.

Sing \w praises|strong="H3068"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*! Sing \w praises|strong="H3068"\w*! Sing \w praises|strong="H3068"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w our|strong="H3068"\w* King! Sing \w praises|strong="H3068"\w*!

\w For|strong="H4428"\w* God \w is|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H2167"\w* \w King|strong="H4428"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* all \w the|strong="H2167"\w* earth. \w Sing|strong="H2167"\w* \w praises|strong="H2167"\w* \w with|strong="H4428"\w* understanding.
God reigns \w over|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* nations. God sits \w on|strong="H3605"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* holy throne.

\w The|strong="H5921"\w* princes \w of|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* peoples \w are|strong="H1471"\w* \w gathered|strong="H1471"\w* \w together|strong="H5921"\w*, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w people|strong="H1471"\w* \w of|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* God \w of|strong="H3427"\w* Abraham. \w For|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* shields \w of|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* earth belong \w to|strong="H5921"\w* God. \w He|strong="H5921"\w* \w is|strong="H3678"\w* greatly exalted!
